&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing and implementing ML models and maintaining relevant data in AWS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with DevOps to enable your team access to the tools they need&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributing to every part of the machine learning product lifecycle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of implementing data engineering best practices in all aspects of the data pipeline, i.e. ETL, data integrity, and monitoring&lt;/li&gt;
